cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing tasks such as pronoun prediction. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves the use of deep recurrent neural networks for classification. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves the use of neural networks, and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as it deals with the classification of text data.
